"both use Vulkan NDCs with a Z-range of ``[0.0, 1.0]``. In contrast, the "
"Compatibility renderer uses OpenGL NDCs with a Z-range of ``[-1.0, 1.0]``. "
"For the Compatibility renderer, replace the NDC calculation with this "
"instead:"
